<% content_for :title, "SpeakFlow | 관리자 첨삭 정산 미리보기" %>

<main class="page">
  <section class="surface surface--preview-admin">
    <div class="container surface__inner">
      <div class="admin-preview-shell">
        <%= render "preview/admin/admin/nav" %>

        <section class="admin-preview-main">
          <section class="page-section">
            <div class="section-heading">
              <p class="eyebrow">Preview admin</p>
              <h1 class="section-title">첨삭 정산 테스트 페이지</h1>
              <p class="section-copy">첨삭 상품과 Coach 포함 첨삭은 완료 건별 매출을 기준으로 집계하고, 플랫폼 수수료 10%를 공제한 뒤 강사에게 90%를 정산하는 시안입니다.</p>
            </div>
          </section>

          <section class="page-section">
            <div class="stats-grid">
              <article class="stat-card">
                <span class="stat-card__value"><%= number_to_currency(@coaching_sales_total, unit: "₩", precision: 0) %></span>
                <span class="stat-card__label">첨삭 총매출</span>
              </article>
              <article class="stat-card">
                <span class="stat-card__value"><%= number_to_currency(@coaching_platform_fee, unit: "₩", precision: 0) %></span>
                <span class="stat-card__label">플랫폼 수수료 10%</span>
              </article>
              <article class="stat-card">
                <span class="stat-card__value"><%= number_to_currency(@coaching_instructor_total, unit: "₩", precision: 0) %></span>
                <span class="stat-card__label">강사 지급 총액 90%</span>
              </article>
              <article class="stat-card">
                <span class="stat-card__value"><%= @coaching_settlements.sum { |row| row[:completed_requests] } %>건</span>
                <span class="stat-card__label">완료 첨삭 건수</span>
              </article>
            </div>
          </section>

          <section class="page-section">
            <article class="surface-card admin-preview-panel">
              <h3>첨삭 정산 규칙</h3>
              <div class="admin-preview-flow">
                <span class="admin-preview-step">첨삭 결제금액 집계</span>
                <span class="admin-preview-step">플랫폼 10% 공제</span>
                <span class="admin-preview-step">강사 90% 정산</span>
                <span class="admin-preview-step">완료 건 기준 승인</span>
              </div>
              <div class="admin-preview-note">
                <strong>정책 메모</strong>
                <p>Coach 포함 첨삭도 완료 건수 기준으로 강사 정산 대상에 포함합니다. 상품별 단가가 다를 경우 상품 원가를 별도로 두고 같은 90/10 비율로 분배하는 방향을 상정합니다.</p>
              </div>
            </article>
          </section>

          <section class="page-section">
            <div class="admin-preview-table admin-preview-table--settlements">
              <div class="admin-preview-table__row admin-preview-table__row--head">
                <span>강사</span>
                <span>완료 건수</span>
                <span>총매출</span>
                <span>플랫폼 10%</span>
                <span>강사 지급액</span>
              </div>
              <% @coaching_settlements.each do |row| %>
                <div class="admin-preview-table__row admin-preview-table__row--settlement">
                  <span><strong><%= row[:instructor] %></strong></span>
                  <span><%= row[:completed_requests] %>건</span>
                  <span><%= number_to_currency(row[:gross], unit: "₩", precision: 0) %></span>
                  <span>- <%= number_to_currency(row[:platform_fee], unit: "₩", precision: 0) %></span>
                  <span><strong><%= number_to_currency(row[:payout], unit: "₩", precision: 0) %></strong></span>
                </div>
              <% end %>
            </div>
          </section>
        </section>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</main>
